data.description: Beautifully custom built 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home! Step out to a concrete driveway, inviting sidewalk, and southern stamped concrete porch. Walk into 12ft ceilings, marble tile, and hardwood floors. Gorgeous thick crown molding throughout home. Living room has warm inviting fireplace. Home was built with 2x6 framing. Has a walkout basement with the coolest 1950's working kitchen with soda style island & stool tops. Other features include 2 gas fireplaces, jetted tub, walk in shower, safe room in basement, butler pantry and more! 2023-01-29
